    <name>UMLet</name>
    <developer_name>umlet</developer_name>
    <summary> Free UML Tool for Fast UML Diagrams </summary>
    <description>
        <p>UMLet is an open-source UML tool with a simple user interface: draw UML diagrams fast, export diagrams to eps, pdf, jpg, svg, and clipboard, share diagrams using Eclipse, and create new, custom UML elements.</p>
        <p>
        NOTE: This is an unofficial package based on the official zip-file releases from www.umlet.com.
        </p>
    </description>

